{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Monsieur le chancelier,", "start": 0.06, "duration": 1.26}, {"text": "parlons nous franchement,", "start": 1.32, "duration": 0.54}, {"text": "les divergences entre nos pays", "start": 1.86, "duration": 1.44}, {"text": "deviennent souvent inqui\u00e9tantes.", "start": 3.3, "duration": 1.26}, {"text": "Le mien,", "start": 4.56, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "la France, a sa responsabilit\u00e9,", "start": 5.16, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "mais derri\u00e8re les mots,", "start": 6.06, "duration": 1.08}, {"text": "votre coalition finit", "start": 7.14, "duration": 1.56}, {"text": "par mettre l'Europe en danger.", "start": 8.7, "duration": 1.26}, {"text": "Vous parlez d'Europe unie,", "start": 9.96, "duration": 1.38}, {"text": "mais apr\u00e8s avoir impos\u00e9", "start": 11.34, "duration": 1.56}, {"text": "l'aust\u00e9rit\u00e9 partout,", "start": 12.9, "duration": 0.78}, {"text": "vous lancez le \u201cDoppelwumms\u201d", "start": 13.68, "duration": 1.38}, {"text": "sans pr\u00e9venir personne", "start": 15.06, "duration": 1.02}, {"text": "\u2013 un plan de soutien", "start": 16.08, "duration": 1.14}, {"text": "massif pour l'\u00e9conomie allemande,", "start": 17.22, "duration": 1.02}, {"text": "et tant pis", "start": 18.24, "duration": 0.48}, {"text": "pour les autres pays europ\u00e9ens", "start": 18.72, "duration": 1.26}, {"text": "qui en sortiront", "start": 19.98, "duration": 0.78}, {"text": "durablement d\u00e9stabilis\u00e9s.", "start": 20.76, "duration": 1.44}, {"text": "Vous dites que nous devons parler", "start": 22.2, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "d'une seule voix,", "start": 23.4, "duration": 0.54}, {"text": "mais vous aller seul en Chine", "start": 23.94, "duration": 0.96}, {"text": "pour y maintenir vos positions,", "start": 24.9, "duration": 1.14}, {"text": "au prix de nos d\u00e9pendances.", "start": 26.04, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "Vous parlez de solidarit\u00e9,", "start": 27.84, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": "mais quand vous fermez,", "start": 29.16, "duration": 0.96}, {"text": "en pleine crise de l'\u00e9nergie,", "start": 30.12, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": "votre derni\u00e8re centrale nucl\u00e9aire,", "start": 31.44, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "c'est dans tous nos pays", "start": 32.94, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "que les factures s'alourdissent.", "start": 34.44, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "Vos \u00e9lus font, ici, tout pour asphyxier", "start": 35.64, "duration": 2.76}, {"text": "cette fili\u00e8re,", "start": 38.4, "duration": 0.42}, {"text": "au nom de l'\u00e9cologie, para\u00eet-il...", "start": 38.82, "duration": 1.56}, {"text": "Mais vos ministres agrandissent", "start": 40.38, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "les mines de charbon en Allemagne,", "start": 42.18, "duration": 1.14}, {"text": "et c'est toute l'Europe qu'ils polluent.", "start": 43.32, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "Vous dites que l'Europe doit ma\u00eetriser", "start": 45.12, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "les flux migratoires,", "start": 46.62, "duration": 0.72}, {"text": "mais vous faites tout", "start": 47.34, "duration": 0.66}, {"text": "pour les augmenter en Allemagne.", "start": 48.0, "duration": 1.44}, {"text": "Vous avez dit, Monsieur", "start": 49.44, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": "le chancelier : \u201cAucun d'entre nous", "start": 50.76, "duration": 1.38}, {"text": "ne veut revenir", "start": 52.14, "duration": 0.48}, {"text": "\u00e0 l'\u00e9poque o\u00f9 la loi du plus fort", "start": 52.62, "duration": 1.68}, {"text": "r\u00e9gnait en Europe\u201d.", "start": 54.3, "duration": 1.02}, {"text": "Ce ne peut pas \u00eatre que des mots...", "start": 55.32, "duration": 2.34}, {"text": "[en allemand] Hannah Arendt \u00e9crivait :\u00a0\n\"Une crise ne devient une catastrophe", "start": 57.66, "duration": 3.948}, {"text": "que si nous y r\u00e9pondons", "start": 61.608, "duration": 8.994}, {"text": "par des id\u00e9es\u00a0toutes\u00a0faites.\"", "start": 70.602, "duration": 1.672}, {"text": "Monsieur le chancelier,", "start": 72.274, "duration": 1.202}, {"text": "il est grand temps", "start": 73.476, "duration": 0.94}, {"text": "de nous remettre\u00a0en\u00a0question.", "start": 74.416, "duration": 1.62}, {"text": "Merci beaucoup.", "start": 76.036, "duration": 0.784}]}